snippet.title: ETHEREAL - Official Gameplay Trailer.
snippet.description:
Avaiable on itch.io: https://caiogui.itch.io/ethereal
Ethereal is a 3D Platformer Collect-a-thon free to play game.  

After several years, your time to evolve to a higher plane has finally come, but first you must collect all the fragments of memories and the special canonic collectibles to surpass all your regrets and learn with yourself for your ascension.
